STATE
v.
Paul Dewayne CUMMINGS. No. 1A05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 8, 2007. Amy C. Kunstling, Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney Generals, Ben David, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 7th day of June 2007 by Defendant to File Supplemental Brief Addressing Uttecht v. Brown as related to issues I and II:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 8th day of June 2007."
